Installation
============
python-django (>1.0) python-support (>= 0.7.1) python-sqlalchemy (>=0.4)  python-psycopg2 postgresql

Warning, some packages must be taken from etch-backports (python-sqlalchemy) or even lenny ( python-django python-support )

Apache
======
Enable ssl and authn_dbd in apache:
a2enmod ssl dbd authn_dbd

Generate self-signed certificate:
openssl req -nodes -x509 -days 3650 -new -newkey rsa:2048 -subj /CN=nike.fr.gl3 -keyout nike.key -out nike.crt

Listen on port 443
Add a new line "Listen 443" to /etc/apache2/ports.conf"

